among the tigers but they say they are prepared to return to the 
jungle 
we are giving him all the opportunities we can stanley 
dominic a senior guerrilla said from the northern tigerheld town 
of jaffna if he doesnt use them properly and as a result there 
is another war we are prepared for it 
